      "comment_id" : 112266334,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "The <a href=\"https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-951\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">issue</a>  is marked as Solved but as the last comment states, it&#39;s still occurring. I have it in version <code>3.0.0-M4</code>. This fixed it."
